Class TinkerMinimizationJob

  • java.lang.Object
    • TinkerMinimizationJob
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Immutable, java.io.Serializable, java.util.concurrent.Callable<Result>, WorkUnit

    public class TinkerMinimizationJob
extends java.lang.Object
implements WorkUnit, java.io.Serializable, Immutable
    This class represents a TINKER minimization job. It is assumed that TINKER is in the path. On Cygwin, check that the executable files end in .exe.
